        "identifier" : "changeNote",
        "language" : "en",
        "value" : "**Version 2 Changelog** Introduction of four aspects: - hasForm ObjectProperty deprecated; NotionalEkphrasis and MimeticEkphrasis classes become subClassOf Ekphrasis - Aligment of Ekphrasis with CIDOC-CRM instantiated as subClassOf E33_Linguistic_Object - Transition to SKOS Concept to identify the ekphrastic modelities (denotation, dynamization, integration), prior modeled as classes - Definition of an ObjectProperty hasAuthor for signaling the author of Ekphrasis, more specifical than dct:creator",
